And yet,


The Eſſence is virtually the Subſistency;


The Subſiſtency is virtually the Energie;


The Energie is virtually the Operation:

Becauſe,


The Eſſence is the Abyſſe from whence the Subſistencies Emane;

The Subſiſtencies are the Fountains from which the Energies flow;

The Energies are the Cauſes (in the Subject) of all Operations.

In like manner,


The Operation is not the Energie;


The Energie is not the Subſistency;


The Subſiſtency is not the Eſſence:

And yet,


The Operation is relatively the Energie;


The Energie is relatively the Subſistency;


The Subſiſtency is relatively the Eſſence.

Becauſe,


The Operations (in the ſubject) are the Energies terminated;

The Energies are the Subſiſtencies limited;

The Subſiſtencies are the Eſſence ſpecificated.
